sentences: J. C. Jones (born 1973) is an American country music artist.
Jones was signed to a recording deal with Rising Tide Records and released his debut album, One Night, in 1998.
When Rising Tide closed in March 1998, he no longer had a record label deal.
Jones was signed to a recording deal with Rising Tide Records and released his debut album, One Night, in 1998.
The "One Night" single was produced by Emory Gordy Jr. and Steve Fishell, and written by Lewis Storey, Rick Carnes, and Janis Carnes.
